Thieves Steal Diamonds From Baselworld, Tages-Anzeiger Reports

-- B y   C a r o l y n   B a n d e l
-- 
2011-03-30T15:48:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-30/thieves-steal-diamonds-from-baselworld-tages-anzeiger-reports.html
Thieves stole four diamonds worth
“several million Swiss francs” around 11 a.m. local time today
from Baselworld in  Basel ,  Switzerland , Tages-Anzeiger  reported ,
citing a spokesman for the world’s largest watch fair.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carolyn Bandel in Zurich at 
 cbandel@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net . 